						<p>Veggie Box<br>25</p> <button class="ml-10 button button-blue purchase" id="veggie" onclick="buyBox(this.id)">Buy</button>
					</div>	
					<p class="text-sm">This box has no Rare Vukkies but way more Mythical<br> and Godly Vukkies!<br>Unique: Salad Vukky, Vukky Planet</p>
				</div></td>
				</tr>

			<tr>
				<td><div class="rounded-lg py-10 px-10 m-10 bg-gray-200 bg-opacity-30">
					<img class="max-h-48" src="./resources/firevukkybox.webp"/>
					<div class="inline-flex justify-between">
						<p>FIRE Box<br>25</p> <button class="ml-10 button button-blue purchase" id="fire" onclick="buyBox(this.id)">Buy</button>
					</div>	
